        ("Positive Feedback Switch", "Strong positive autoregulation", "What do you predict happens when a protein activates its own gene — does expression stabilize at a higher level or does something more interesting happen?"),
        ("Epigenetic Silencing", "Closed chromatin, high transcription factor", "Do you predict that a high concentration of Transcription Factor can overcome epigenetic silencing of the target gene?")
