        ("Disciplinary Core Idea", "ESS3.D Global Climate Change / LS2.C Ecosystem Dynamics, Functioning, and Resilience", "Human activities affect global climate through greenhouse gas emissions; ecosystems respond to climate disruption through species migration, productivity changes, and potential collapse when adaptation limits are exceeded."),
